Industry Press Releases





EVRAZ North America plc Announces First Quarter 2017 Conference Call Schedule 

Monday, May 29, 2017



EVRAZ North America plc announced that in connection with the 7.5% Senior Secured Notes due 2019 issued by its subsidiary EVRAZ Inc. NA Canada, it will conduct a conference call on Wednesday, May 31st, 2017 at 12:00 P.M. Eastern time to discuss its first quarter 2017 financial results.
The Company invites holders of the notes, prospective investors, broker dealers, and fixed income securities analysts to join the call. Please contact EVRAZ North America Investor Relations to obtain information about joining the call.
About EVRAZ
EVRAZ North America plc (the Company) is a wholly owned subsidiary of EVRAZ plc, one of the largest vertically integrated steel and mining businesses in the world. The Company is a leading North American producer of engineered steel products for rail, energy and industrial end markets. The Company has six production sites located in the USA (Portland, Oregon; Pueblo, Colorado) and Canada (Regina, Saskatchewan; Calgary, Camrose and Red Deer, Alberta).
Contacts
Investor Relations Contact:
EVRAZ North America plc
Christian Messmacher
Vice President – Investor Relations
IR@evrazna.com
312-533-3520
 
Source:businesswire.com





 



























