Evraz

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


EVRAZ plc





Type

Public limited company


Traded as
LSE: EVR


Industry
Steel
Mining


Founded
1992 (Moscow)


Headquarters
London, United Kingdom



Key people

Alexander Abramov (Chairman)
Aleksandr Frolov (CEO)


Products
Steel
Steel products
Vanadium Slag
Iron ore
Coal


