Evraz North America PLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















evraz north america plc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Iron & Steel
Sub-Industry: Steel Producers
Evraz North America PLC mines and manufactures steel products. The Company offers steel plates, seamless pipes, wire rod and coiled reinforcing bars, line pipe, casting and tubing products, and recycling services. Evraz North America markets its products worldwide.




