EVRAZ North America plc Announces First Quarter 2017 Conference Call Schedule | Business Wire
























































EVRAZ North America plc Announces First Quarter 2017 Conference Call 
      Schedule






May 26, 2017 10:24 AM Eastern Daylight Time



CHICAGO--(BUSINESS WIRE)--EVRAZ North America plc (the Company) announced that in connection with 
      the 7.5% Senior Secured Notes due 2019 issued by its subsidiary EVRAZ 
      Inc. NA Canada, it will conduct a conference call on Wednesday, May 31st, 
      2017 at 12:00 P.M. Eastern time to discuss its first quarter 2017 
      financial results.
    


      The Company invites holders of the notes, prospective investors, broker 
      dealers, and fixed income securities analysts to join the call. Please 
      contact EVRAZ North America Investor Relations to obtain information 
      about joining the call.
    

About EVRAZ


      EVRAZ North America plc (the Company) is a wholly owned subsidiary of 
      EVRAZ plc, one of the largest vertically integrated steel and mining 
      businesses in the world. The Company is a leading North American 
      producer of engineered steel products for rail, energy and industrial 
      end markets. The Company has six production sites located in the USA 
      (Portland, Oregon; Pueblo, Colorado) and Canada (Regina, Saskatchewan; 
      Calgary, Camrose and Red Deer, Alberta).
    

      EVRAZ is a registered trademark of EVRAZ Group S.A.
    


Contacts

Investor Relations Contact:EVRAZ North America plcChristian 
      MessmacherVice President – Investor RelationsIR@evrazna.com312-533-3520
    
















