Technology Centers
Recycling






EVRAZ Portland
Oregon


EVRAZ operates the following facilities in Portland, Oregon:

 Rolling Mill
Spiral Pipe Mill


EVRAZ has the only plate mill in the Western U.S. and adjacent Canadian provinces.  We also operate quench and tempering lines. Our proximity to deep water ports and rail allows us to cost effectively source  domestic or foreign steel slabs.  










