EVRAZ









  


RESPONSIBLE
EMPLOYER OF ABOUT 80,000 PROFESSIONALS
Employees of EVRAZ are integral to the Company’s success. EVRAZ attracts the best and supports their development.






  


EFFICIENT
PRODUCER OF STEEL PRODUCTS FOR INFRASTRUCTURE PROJECTS AROUND THE WORLD
Our steel is used for the construction of railways,
bridges and pipelines, residential and office buildings,
and stadiums.






  


INTERNATIONAL
PRODUCER OF STEEL, IRON ORE AND COAL, OPERATING ON THREE CONTINENTS
EVRAZ - one of the largest steel and mining companies with assets in Russia, Ukraine, the US, Canada, Czech Republic, Italy, and South Africa.






  


GLOBAL
PRODUCER OF VANADIUM AND VANADIUM PRODUCTS
EVRAZ is one of the largest vanadium producers in the world, and the only producer of vanadium iron ore in Russia.






  


LEADING
GLOBAL PRODUCER OF RAILS
EVRAZ is the second largest steel producer in South Africa, and a leader in the production of large diameter pipes in North America











